      • getSdkSettings

        @Deprecated
void getSdkSettings()
        Deprecated. 
        Retrieves the SdkSettings.

        This method is typically called when you do not care about the result. This is typically the case for the ConfigurationIntentService which attempts to get new settings but fails silently.

        Deprecated, please use getSettings(com.zendesk.sdk.network.impl.ZendeskCallback) with a null callback.
